This is one of 4 projects I’ve been working on over the past few weeks (at the same time😅) 
But honestly I love practicing and challenging my versatility🤘🏼
Here’s a list of what I’ve worked on in the last few weeks-
Switching between stainless tig, mild steel mig, both mig and tig aluminum, spray painting in our paint booth as well as spraying urathane coating, assembling gears and shafts to a motor for what started as 2 hand cranked rotation carts, bending, drilling and all the other random day to day stuff💪🏼😅 
Oh and not to mention that my garden is flourishing and all the other things life throws at us😅
